<div id="main" class="col-md-9" role="main">

# Computes fishing mortality from abundances, catches and natural mortality

<div class="ref-description section level2">

Objects or class 'FLStock' already contain a 'harvest' slot to store
estimates of fishing mortality at age, for example those obtained from a
stock assessment method. Fishing mortality at age can be recalculated
using two methods:

</div>

<div class="section level2">

## Usage

<div class="sourceCode">

``` r
# S4 method for class 'FLStock,missing'
computeHarvest(object, units = NULL)
```

</div>

</div>

<div class="section level2">

## Arguments

-   units:

    Harvest to be computed as 'f' or 'hr', 'character'.

-   x:

    An object of class 'FLStock'.

</div>

<div class="section level2">

## Value

An 'FLQuant' with the calculated fishing mortalities at age.

</div>

<div class="section level2">

## See also

<div class="dont-index">

[FLStock](FLStock.md) `harvest()` [FLQuant](FLQuant.md)

</div>

</div>

<div class="section level2">

## Author

The FLR Team

</div>

<div class="section level2">
